name: Ready for Takeoff
description:
This is our first album, Ready for Takeoff. We are now officially taking orders! Our cd release show will be on August 4th, at Compass Christian (formerly Highland Meadows) on Pool and Hall Johnson Rd. starting at 6:30. It is a FREE show, and a great place to get your copy!

We can also ship your cd to you for a flat rate of 5.00. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact me at willydavidk@gmail.com.

name: Jet-Set T-Shirt
description:
The Jet-Set T-Shirts are finally in print, and are available for sale online!! Feel free to order here, and shoot me an email at willydavidk@gmail.com so I can get you a shirt or ship it to your house, whichever you prefer.

We are currently sold out of T-shirts, but if you really have your heart set on a T-shirt, contact me at the above email, and we may be able to work something out.

name: Pink T-shirt!
description:
By popular demand, we are now officially printing Pink Jet-Set Pilots Tees!! Available in Small or Medium.

We are currently sold out of T-Shirts. However, if you really have your heart set on one, contact me at willydavidk@gmail.com and we'll see if we can work something out.
